# Business social media posts

>* This prompt helps people create posts for businesses on social media

## Overview
This prompt produces a image of a post to help businesses that are short on time reach out to the community

It solves the problem of time and businesses not having time to post things

**Best For :**
- marketing
- prototyping for different posts
- Designing Ads

**Output**
-
- A typical output looks like an image of a post that has the same colors and design types you ask for 
- ## Quick Start
### 1. Copy the prompt
Create a social media post on [social media platform] for a business called [business
name] that sells [what the business sells], make the design of it more [modern, rustic,
etc] and have it appeal to [teens, older people, parents, etc]. The main colors of this
post should be [color pallet] and make the text on the post be clear and centered around
the product that's being sold. I want the length of the post to be [length of post]
### 2. Fill in placeholders
Replace these with your specific information:
- [social media platform] - what social media platform you are making the post for
- [business name] - the name of your business
- [what the business sells] - what your business sells
- [modern, rustic, etc] - what you want your design to look like
- [teens, older people, parents, ect] - who you want to appeal to/ your clientele
- [color pallet] - what colors you want for this post
- [length of post] - how many letters or words you want in the post

